    "term": "counter e.m.f.",
    "source_id": "theory-calculation-alternating-current-phenomena",
    "modern_equivalent": "back EMF, induced opposing voltage, or a phasor voltage-drop representation depending on context",
    "occurrence_count_in_ocr": 82,
    "steinmetz_usage": "Used both for machine-generated opposing electromotive force and, in vector circuit calculation, for the counter e.m.f. of resistance, reactance, and impedance.",
